channel.title: Changing floors in client
channel.description: I'm using Toms cache suite to chage floors. I want to take out some carpets but they aren't in the list of floors. How do you go about editing certain things that aren't found on the floor list?

item.title: Changing floors in client
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

zRickyz:

I’m using Toms cache suite to chage floors. I want to take out some carpets but they aren’t in the list of floors. How do you go about editing certain things that aren’t found on the floor list?

In that case, it’s an object (that doesn’t have a name) so you’ll need to find it yourself (or just remove the object at the specified location)
